Photo Free Usage Agreemnt 

Ⅰ Foreword
1.We use PFUA agreement short for the name 'Photo Free Usage Agreement'.
2.This agreement is normally used by Lixuan's pictures, anyone who wants to use it can add lines such as 
'Using PFUA agreement for the pictures' 
to conform that you know that you use PFUA agreement for your pictures.
3.The writers of this agreement will not be responsible for the photos following the agreement.

Ⅱ Agreement
1.Photos following the agreement can be used by others including 
Printing,sending,making jokes,using in pictures cna PPT's
BUT,if the people in the photo don't agree to be on these occasions, people can't use these photos.
2.Photos following the agreement shouldn't be used commercially.
